<template lang="pug">
.song-list
   ul(v-for="(song, id) in currentPlaylist")
    li index: {{ id}}
    li videoId: {{ song.videoId }}
    li name: {{ song.name }}
</template>
<script>
import { mapState } from 'pinia'
import { usePlaylistStore } from '../store/playlist'
export default {
  computed: {
    ...mapState(usePlaylistStore, ['currentPlaylist'])
  },
}
</script>

<style></style>
